Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, everyone here knows Miller.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was scouted while performing here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Generation Bleu, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's really no mistake, Gazelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miller and her band are...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.87,0:01:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear about that here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:02:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but a company like GenBlu signing a musician directly is a bit strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, GenBlu HQ is a big city where tens of thousands of people live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they said it's just a six month contract...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly do you guys want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The identity of the woman named Miller!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Miller, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This proves Miller the singer really exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole thing is nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever been to one of her shows?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so passionate and sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to her, that girl is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, just a little female geek.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Elena Peoples' birthplace?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Respond to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that another comic book quote?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any Secrets around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no mistake that a Scub Burst has occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pillars of light that come with the emergences of Scub Corals and Secrets have been sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Secret is definitely closing in on the Scub.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering for a while, but what exactly are those pillars of light?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, that's a—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do the Scub and the Secrets come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are multiple theories in regards to the origin of Secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But researchers have yet to reach a consensus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are theories that state that the \Naggregation of trapar in the atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is a natural phenomenon due to chemical reactions,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while others state that in parallel to our world, there is—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My nose! My nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to take forever, so save it for another time, Fukai Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dust filter can't take much more. Return for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got visual on the Scub Coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't see any signs of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no data on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be that Truth guy again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't enter the ZOA carelessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have yet to detect any signs of the Secret or Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You okay, Georg?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not acting strange because I hit you earlier, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, you broke him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd Truth go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I saw him. He was huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still worried about your little girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty annoying today, Fleur.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have a fight with Mr. Papa again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call him that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just asked her how things are going with Ao lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just doesn't understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao and me? That's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like half my age!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention he's in love with his little girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Fleur already has someone else she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away this time, Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The President?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid dad! Stupid dad! Stupid dad! Stupid dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Genten Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unclear if we managed to drive the Secret back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retrieving the Quartz and confirming that the Burst has calmed down will be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be safe, I'll tell the Australian army to remain alert, not alarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... are you surprised, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Blanc! Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! What have you found in your investigation so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The facility is locked down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no surprise there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard by the time we took Elena in, most of the children were already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of facility is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no data on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that some children are born with the ability to pilot IFOs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not yet proven,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it is widely believed that being born in an area with high trapar density
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,causes changes in brain structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children like that were gathered and researched in many countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That place is one such lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena was raised in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still think she and Miller are one and the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen the security footage too, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are well aware of the unusual activities of our company's contracted artist, Miller Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From her communication records, we suspect she's an American spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:09:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miller Joe being the same person as Elena Peoples is just your theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena has undergone training in our company for over two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she debut as an indie artist in Manchester...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if she was undergoing IFO pilot training 1300km away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gazelle, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what Truth said?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth only shows itself to the ones who try to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that this world is wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that I can't see the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it, but I don't like it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters, 20 floors underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as far as the emergency staircase takes me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's clear that it goes even further down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are clearly traces of another culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One different from ours... Something from a different world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me this isn't Miller?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Miller is an agent we've selected carefully in cooperation with the British intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had prepared her so that she could get contracted with Generation Bleu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember. Our IFO budget was cut thanks to that stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have all her physical data on file, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She does indeed look very similar, but there are slight differences in the voiceprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ordered my man who works as her producer to procure saliva samples,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we checked for DNA matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are totally different people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:11:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For at least two months, the person we have been in contact with was not Miller.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're going to have to remove the outer armor to clean the sand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long is Stanley going to be our substitute chief for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been graphing your weight gains! He's obviously teasing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not the only one who got fatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one like Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I wish I could hug his big bear belly again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, has team Goldilocks been ordered to scramble?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bruno!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... Miller...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... Elena...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miller!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth got away today, but I'll find him eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, we're leaving together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've been waiting! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sky of Iwato Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Noah? Where's Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Goldilocks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you still trying to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a bear! It's my Hans!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alex! Are the children all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The systems have been shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're opening the canopies now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Bring all three of them here right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama! I must save Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama! Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's confirmed that oxygen inhalation eases the hallucinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama! Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Georg deduced, the trapar in the air is the cause of the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those particles react with the trapar in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after entering their bodies, stimulating the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has no effect on us, but it causes hallucinations to the \Nchildren whose brain structures have been altered by trapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strengthen the filters of all air conditioning units to filter out trapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we have to figure out how to get rid of the particles in their bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that every one of those particles is a Secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Ao and Elena going to be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's different from us on a genetic level.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao and Elena, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you tell me before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you wanted to see the real thing, not just a broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:17:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only adults can come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miller, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been? What are you doing taking to the stage by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been summoned. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao! Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, we must run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't I just in Generation Bleu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been misleading us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our world is outside here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, we'll lead you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must search for it... Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ryukyu SDF? It's the men of Pippo's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena, take care of Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does a Pied Piper pilot disguise herself as Miller and send us intel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it fake intel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that can't be. Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, once we're in the real world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we won't have to fight ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop already, Miller.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you're triggering your death flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Miller is—?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we fire warning shots?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car's AC filter is filtering out trapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Ao, Elena?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them fool you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving! Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it! A different world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One that's outside of this boring world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what you've been looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll take you away from this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, we look so similar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we were related in our past life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena! Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy spy has infiltrated our base!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that you were triggering your death flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah! Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you sure that they're two different people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They existed at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That said, Miller's just a pile of ashes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't finance any further investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, President! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad. We finally found someone who knew the Peoples.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about what she's been through before she entered the facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you bringing up Mistress Elena's accident again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're reopening the investigation, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five years ago on a Caribbean sea cruise,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Mistress was caught up in a Scub Burst...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master grieved greatly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He even fell ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena Peoples is... a Generat—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... That was taken a year before Mistress Elena died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then... who's the current Elena Peoples?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena! You should be in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just watering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did feel down, but I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet dreams, Miller.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.63,0:22:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet dreams, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.55,0:22:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.87,0:24:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Eureka Seven AO.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pied Piper goes into space with the whole world's eyes on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao faces a new challenge fighting in zero gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will the appearance of the silver wings at a decisive moment show him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.07,0:24:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Eureka Seven AO,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.98,0:24:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,episode 12: Step into a World.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.56,0:24:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to the voices of the children of the stars.
